Bluehost提供各种主机解决方案，包括{{link-en|共享主机|Shared web hosting service}}、[[WordPress|WordPress]]主机、[[虚拟专用服务器|虚拟专用服务器]]、[[专有服务器|专有服务器]]和{{link-en|WooCommerce}}主机以及专业营销服务。Bluehost的服务器采用[[PHP|PHP]]、[[HTTP/2|HTTP/2]]和[[Nginx|Nginx]][[缓存|缓存]]<ref>{{Cite news|title=Bluehost Review|author=Website Hosting Rating|url=https://www.websitehostingrating.com/bluehost-review/|accessdate=2021-03-13|archive-date=2020-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200331021740/https://www.websitehostingrating.com/bluehost-review/}}</ref>。在台灣, Bluehost 主機會寄發統一發票 (收據)，但是無法輸入統一編號, 可以使用這個統一發票(收據)去報帳，但是無法拿來抵稅。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Bluehost 主機：可以打台灣統編報稅嗎？|url=https://wpointer.com/wordpress-tutorials/wordpress-development/hosting-domain/bluehost-tax-exemption/|access-date=2022-01-25|date=2021-07-29|last=|first=|work=|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2022-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220125162109/https://wpointer.com/wordpress-tutorials/wordpress-development/hosting-domain/bluehost-tax-exemption/}}</ref>

